==安全性==

临床实验显示，健康人类可以每日安全服用 300 mg 四甲尿酸持续 8 周，且不会产生习惯。<ref name="pmid26766930">{{cite journal | vauthors = Taylor L, Mumford P, Roberts M, Hayward S, Mullins J, Urbina S, Wilborn C | title = Safety of TeaCrine®, a non-habituating, naturally-occurring purine alkaloid over eight weeks of continuous use | journal = Journal of the International Society of Sports Nutrition | volume = 13 | issue =  | pages = 2 | year = 2016 | pmid = 26766930 | pmc = 4711067 | doi = 10.1186/s12970-016-0113-3 | url = http://jissn.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12970-016-0113-3 | accessdate = 2016-05-14 | quote = <small><br/>• These findings support the clinical safety and non-habituating neuro-energetic effects of TeaCrine® supplementation over 8 weeks of daily use (up to 300 mg/day). Moreover, there was no evidence of a tachyphylactic response that is typical of neuroactive agents such as caffeine and other stimulants.<br/>• Specifically, the acute toxicity for theacrine ingestion in mice has been previously reported [4] to be an LD50 of 810.6 mg/kg, which would equate to roughly 4.0 g for an individual weighing 76 kg.</small> | archive-date = 2016-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160604111714/http://jissn.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12970-016-0113-3 | dead-url = no }}</ref>实验中未发现四甲尿酸具有咖啡因等其他兴奋剂的{{tsl|en|tachyphylaxis|快速耐受|}}现象。<ref name="pmid26766930"/>

在动物实验中，四甲尿酸的[[半數致死量|LD<sub>50</sub>]]为 810 mg/kg，<ref name="pmid20227468">{{cite journal | vauthors = Wang Y, Yang X, Zheng X, Li J, Ye C, Song X | title = Theacrine, a purine alkaloid with anti-inflammatory and analgesic activities | journal = Fitoterapia | volume = 81 | issue = 6 | pages = 627–31 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20227468 | doi = 10.1016/j.fitote.2010.03.008 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Xiao_Rong_Yang/publication/41942987_Theacrine_a_purine_alkaloid_with_anti-inflammatory_and_analgesic_activities/links/560ba2a508ae576ce6412343.pdf | accessdate = 2016-05-15 | quote = <small>the result of the acute toxicity test showed that the LD(50) of theacrine was 810.6 mg/kg (769.5-858.0mg/kg).</small> | archive-date = 2017-09-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170901024656/https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Xiao_Rong_Yang/publication/41942987_Theacrine_a_purine_alkaloid_with_anti-inflammatory_and_analgesic_activities/links/560ba2a508ae576ce6412343.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="pmid26766930"/>高于咖啡因的 265 mg/kg。<ref name="pmid698326">{{cite journal | vauthors = Warszawski D, Gorodischer R, Kaplanski J | title = Comparative toxicity of caffeine and aminophylline (theophylline ethylenediamine) in young and adult rats | journal = Biology of the Neonate | volume = 34 | issue = 1-2 | pages = 68–71 | year = 1978 | pmid = 698326 | doi = 10.1159/000241107| url = | quote = <small>In adult rats, the LD50 of caffeine and aminophylline was the same after 24 h and after 1 week of observation: caffeine 265 mg/kg</small>}}</ref>

